  • Boruta feature selection

train.clean = read.csv("../data/trainCleaned.csv") 

#=============================================
# Boruta feature selection based on train data
#=============================================
features = setdiff(names(train.clean),c("X", "Id", "SalePrice", 
                                   "YrSold", "MoSold"))
response = train.clean$SalePrice
set.seed(0)
bor.results = Boruta(train.clean[features], response, 
                      maxRuns=101, doTrace=0)
plot(bor.results)

save(bor.results, file="../result/2.boruta.rda")
bor.sel = getSelectedAttributes(bor.results, withTentative = F)
getSelectedAttributes(bor.results)
##  [1] "MSZoning"      "LotShape"      "LandContour"   "Neighborhood" 
##  [5] "BldgType"      "HouseStyle"    "Exterior1st"   "Exterior2nd"  
##  [9] "ExterQual"     "Foundation"    "BsmtQual"      "BsmtExposure" 
## [13] "BsmtFinType1"  "HeatingQC"     "CentralAir"    "KitchenQual"  
## [17] "Functional"    "FireplaceQu"   "GarageType"    "GarageFinish" 
## [21] "GarageQual"    "GarageCond"    "PavedDrive"    "SaleCondition"
## [25] "GarageYrBlt"   "MSSubClass"    "LotArea"       "OverallQual"  
## [29] "OverallCond"   "YearBuilt"     "YearRemodAdd"  "BsmtFinSF1"   
## [33] "BsmtUnfSF"     "TotalBsmtSF"   "X1stFlrSF"     "X2ndFlrSF"    
## [37] "GrLivArea"     "BsmtFullBath"  "FullBath"      "HalfBath"     
## [41] "BedroomAbvGr"  "KitchenAbvGr"  "TotRmsAbvGrd"  "Fireplaces"   
## [45] "GarageCars"    "GarageArea"    "WoodDeckSF"    "OpenPorchSF"  
## [49] "LotFrontage"   "MasVnrArea"    "Electrical"
train.sel = train.clean[, bor.sel] %>% 
  cbind(train.clean[, names(train.clean) %in% 
                      c("SalePrice", "YrSold", "MoSold")]) %>% 
  mutate(t = as.yearmon(paste(train.clean$YrSold, train.clean$MoSold, 
                              sep = "-"))) # generate time sold

write.csv(train.sel, "../data/trainSelected.csv")
